	<h2 class="title">Learning Development Centre</h2>

				<a name="SubTitle1"></a>
			
	<h4 class="plain">Training &amp; Meeting Rooms</h4>

				<a name="BodyText1"></a>
			
		<span id="blacktext">
			<P>The Learning Development Centre is a quality but cost effective training venue. The Centre has a number of training / meeting rooms provided with standard training equipment with additional equipment available for hire. There is also an ICT suite with 12 work stations and a conference hall that can seat up to 100 people.</P>
<P>The Centre&rsquo;s facilities include</P>
<UL>
<LI>6 Training Rooms (capacity of up to 30 people)</LI>
<LI>1 ICT suite (with twelve work stations)</LI>
<LI>1 conference hall (up to 100 people)</LI>
<LI>Full on-site catering facilities</LI>
<LI>On site parking </LI>
<LI>Good public transport access</LI>
<LI>Large refreshment and coffee area</LI>
<LI>Additional training equipment for hire</LI></UL>
<P>The Learning Development Centre is open Monday to Friday 8.15am to 6pm, and at other times and days by arrangement. </P>
<P>For additional information and/or booking forms please phone Reception on 01273 293699.</P>
<P>Learning Development Centre <BR>Hodshrove Lane<BR>Moulsecoomb<BR>Brighton<BR>BN2 4SE </P>
